Changes:
 ros-humble-moveit-chomp-optimizer-adapter (3.0.0-2023.03.10.13.11) jammy; urgency=high
 .
   * Fix BSD license in package.xml (#1796 <https://github.com/ros-planning/moveit2/issues/1796>)
